### Copy below line of code for desktop shortcut
nano Burp_Pro_v2023.2.2.desktop
```bash
[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Name=Burp-Pro
Icon=/home/kali/BurpPro/burp_v2023.2.2/burp.png
Exec=/home/kali/BurpPro/burp_v2023.2.2/burp.sh
Name[en_US]=Burpsuite_2023
Terminal=false
StartupNotify=false
```
### Check for burp.sh permission.
or change it to 771.

### Double click on the desktop shortcut to launch the application. Provide neccessary permissions.

### If the Loader.jar does not run properly and shows activation page directly, start the loader.jar in windows VM.
### Click on RUN.
### Copy the licence and paste it in the main application.
### Click on Next, and then Manual Activation.
### and then follow the rest.
